Module detection
Package fr.project.detection.observers

Interface FeatureObserver

All Known Implementing Classes:
ConcatenationObserver, LambdaObserver, NestMemberObserver, RecordObserver, TryWithResourcesObserver
public interface FeatureObserver
A observer that observes the behavior of an Instruction It allows to notify the user when an Instruction is detected in the .class file. This class is used by the classes MyMethodVisitor and MyClassVisitor.
Author:
SIMONNOT Florent
